{"tid":312011,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【九月歐美推「王者榮耀」國際版】","createTime":"2017-07-07T05:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T13:57:30.000Z","uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b59c52a4a6250af1e9b1c5283d92849eee83056d","tid":312011,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"【九月歐美推「王者榮耀」國際版】<br />\n【與Warner Bros合作　新角色：蝙蝠俠】<br />\n彭博引述消息稱，騰訊計劃最快在九月，於歐美推出「王者榮耀」國際版。<br />\n部分遊戲角色會包括其他卡通人物，包括與華納兄弟（Warner Bros）合作，在遊戲內可以扮演蝙蝠俠。<br />\n目前「王者榮耀」已經在泰國及土耳其推出，之後就會登陸美、法、德、意大利及西班牙等國家。<br />\n報道稱，擴展「王者榮耀」版圖，亦有助減低遊戲在內地面對政策風險。<br />\n人民網早前連續發三篇文章，批評「王者榮耀」毒害玩家，需要加強規管。"},{"pid":"aca1d264ef3fbda3655caa056d4311266541dbed","tid":312011,"uid":108394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0477f92114b070314f6056dc477177b4ad256a75","tid":312011,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fbc6bd8bfb7f4c02f4f133638af6cf1462234cf","tid":312011,"uid":16101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:52:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82b24d5288878eb415be6d0460b5ace35c2bee57","tid":312011,"uid":16101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17f1635dbd23fdbd30880714196157fe73dc23ca","tid":312011,"uid":1156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/195435_4e62841098c4b13e3822b3459ab7e072.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F195435_4e62841098c4b13e3822b3459ab7e072.jpg&h=9858be3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i